<cl=A2A2A2>
Many centuries ago, the best blacksmiths in Sphere founded this guild. In order to make good progress in the Guild, one needs both a serious title and degree. Smithery requires permanent attention, so they don't practice either the magic of elements in the guild or other skills that might be of use in battle. However, there are few who can bear a blow of an experienced blacksmith who, over years of work at the anvil, have acquired not only physical strength, but also magic from the objects he's worked on. Like Armorers, Blacksmiths are recognized as excellent professionals and the Guild's brand alone can guarantee the high quality of armor in Sphere.

<br>
